In a recent issue of the <i><a href="http://www.isreview.org" target="_blank">International Socialist Review</a></i>, Toufic Haddad's article<a href="http://www.isreview.org/issues/49/birthpangs.shtml" target="_blank"> "Birth Pangs of a New Middle East"</a> sets out the backdrop of the Israeli war and analyzes its consequences.<p>
